After having flown past and out of the Oteybis defenses some time ago, 
Hellpeon soon spots Ultimo and laughs evily as he lands. the Tall demonic bot 
smirks as he looks over Ultimo for a moment.

Hellpeon: "Your to be my training partner? Looks more like you would be a 
squire for a fighter."

Hellpeon grins at that as energy begins to crackle around his body as the 
large energy being folds his arms across his chest waiting for the training 
to begin.
